('Hoy cobra tanto sentido este poema Mario Benedetti Cuando la tormenta pase Y se amansen los caminos  y seamos sobrevivientes  de un naufragio colectivo.  Con el corazÃ³n lloroso y el destino bendecido nos sentiremos dichosos tan sÃ³lo por estar vivos. Y le daremos un abrazo  al primer desconocido y alabaremos la suerte de conservar un amigo. Y entonces recordaremos todo aquello que perdimos y de una vez aprenderemos  todo lo que no aprendimos. Ya no tendremos envidia pues todos habrÃ¡n sufrido.  Ya no tendremos desidia  Seremos mÃ¡s compasivos.  ValdrÃ¡ mÃ¡s lo que es de todos  Que lo jamas conseguido Seremos mÃ¡s generosos Y mucho mÃ¡s comprometidos Entenderemos lo frÃ¡gil  que significa estar vivos Sudaremos empatÃ­a  por quien estÃ¡ y quien se ha ido. ExtraÃ±aremos al viejo  que pedÃ­a un peso en el mercado, que no supimos su nombre y siempre estuvo a tu lado. Y quizÃ¡s el viejo pobre era tu Dios disfrazado.  Nunca preguntaste el nombre porque estabas apurado. Y todo serÃ¡ un milagro Y todo serÃ¡ un legado Y se respetarÃ¡ la vida,  la vida que hemos ganado.  Cuando la tormenta pase te pido Dios, apenado,  que nos devuelvas mejores,  como nos habÃ­as soÃ±ado.', "Today this poem makes so much sense Mario Benedetti When the storm passes And the roads are tamed and we are survivors of a collective shipwreck. With a tearful heart and a blessed destiny, we will feel happy just for being alive. And we will give a hug to the first stranger and we will praise the luck of keeping a friend. And then we will remember everything that we lost and at once we will learn everything that we did not learn. We will no longer be envious because everyone will have suffered. We will no longer have apathy We will be more compassionate. What belongs to everyone will be worth more Than ever achieved We will be more generous And much more committed We will understand how fragile it means to be alive We will sweat empathy for who is and who is gone. We will miss the old man who asked for a peso in the market, we didn't know his name and he was always by your side. And maybe the poor old man was your God in disguise. You never asked the name because you were in a hurry. And everything will be a miracle And everything will be a legacy And life will be respected, the life we have earned. When the storm passes I ask God, sorry, that you give us back better, as you had dreamed of us.", [('spa', 1.0)])

 Ninguno de estos productos daÃ±an ni el hÃ­gado ni los riÃ±ones.

Al *lavar la ropa* se pone en la lavadora un poquito de *bicarbonato o de vinagre o de limÃ³n* y no solamente van a estar protegidos contra el virus sino para otro tipo de bacterias.

Ademas estas sustancias como el *bicarbonato con la sal y el limÃ³n* tambiÃ©n eliminan -(y ustedes van a notar que algo flota en el agua)- aquellas productos quÃ­micos que se colocan en las plantas.

======================================

Gereja ini dibangun oleh seorang pendeta yang bernama Franciscan Friar. Material bangunan terbuat dari tengkorak dan tulang belulang kaum Muslimin spanyol yang dibunuh secara massal dan dikuburkan di pekuburan massal dekat bangunan gereja. 

Diantara hiasan penting bangun gereja ini adalah dua mayat muslim utuh yang telah dikeringkan dan digantungkan di dinding gereja menggunakan rantai besi. Dua mayat kering ini adalah dua remaja muslim yang digantung hidup-hidup kemudian dikeringkan dan digantungkan di dinding dalam gereja sebagai dekor gereja tempat beribadat agama ini. 

Gereja Capela dos Ossos ini memuat lebih dari 5 ribu kerangka manusia dari kalangan warga muslim Moriscos asli spanyol yang menolak memeluk kristen setelah spanyol jatuh ke tangan salibis, dan muslim Mariscos dihabisi secara massal. 

Jadi siapa sesungguhnya yang kejam? 

**| Ketika Kekuasaan Islam Berakhir di Spanyol Jutaan Umat Islam Dibantai |

ØªØ±ÙŠØ® Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø³Ù„Ù…ÙˆÙ† ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù†Ø¯Ù„Ø³ÙŠØ§  ( Spanyol Muslim )', 'THIS CHURCH WAS BUILT FROM THOUSANDS OF SKULL AND BONES - THE THINGS OF MUSLIMS WHO WAS SLAPPED FOR refusing to enter the Roman Catholic religion
======================================

This church was built by a priest named Franciscan Friar. The building material is made of skulls and bones of Spanish Muslims who were massacred and buried in mass graves near the church building.

Among the important decorations of this church building are two intact Muslim bodies that have been dried and hung on the church walls using iron chains. These two dried corpses are two Muslim teenagers who were hanged alive and then dried and hung on the walls in the church as a decoration of the church where this religion worships.

The Capela dos Ossos church contains more than 5,000 human skeletons from among the native Spanish Moriscos Muslims who refused to convert to Christianity after Spain fell to the crusaders, and Mariscos Muslims were massacred.

So who really is the cruel one?

**| When Islamic rule ended in Spain, millions of Muslims were massacred |

('Se habla de reanimaciÃ³n o ventilaciÃ³n pero mucha gente no sabe lo que verdad se trata.

No se trata de una mÃ¡scara de oxÃ­geno puesto en la boca mientras usted disfruta acostado pensando en su vida...
La ventilaciÃ³n invasiva para el COVID19 (intubacion que se hace bajo anestesia general ) consiste en quedarse 2 a 3 semanas sin moverse, muchas veces boca abajo (decubitus ventral) con un tubo en la boca hasta la trÃ¡quea y que le permite respirar al ritmo de la mÃ¡quina! a la que esta conectado.
Usted no puede hablar ni comer ni hacer nada de manera natural.
La molestia y el dolor que siente necesitan la administraciÃ³n de sedantes y analgesicos para asegurar la tolerancia al tubo. durante el tiempo que el paciente necesite la maquina para respirar todo esto durante un coma artificial.
En 20 dÃ­as de este tratamiento en un paciente joven la pÃ©rdida de masa muscular es de 40% y la rÃ©Ã©ducacion sera de 6 a 12 meses, asociado a traumatismos de la boca o de las cuerdas vocales.
Es por esta razÃ³n que las personas ancianas o ya frÃ¡giles no aguantan!
.
- Fuente: Natalia Pauly Toloza
.
#covÄ±d19 #cuarentena #vpuanecdotas', "There is talk of resuscitation or ventilation but many people do not know what it really is.

It is not about an oxygen mask put on your mouth while you enjoy lying down thinking about your life...
Invasive ventilation for COVID19 (intubation that is done under general anesthesia) consists of staying 2 to 3 weeks without moving, often face down (ventral decubitus) with a tube in the mouth to the trachea and that allows you to breathe at the rhythm of machine! to which it is connected.
You cannot speak or eat or do anything naturally.
The discomfort and pain you feel require the administration of sedatives and analgesics to ensure tolerance to the tube. during the time that the patient needs the machine to breathe all this during an artificial coma.
In 20 days of this treatment in a young patient, the loss of muscle mass is 40% and the recovery will be from 6 to 12 months, associated with trauma to the mouth or vocal cords.
It is for this reason that elderly or already fragile people can't stand it!
.
- Source: Natalia Pauly Toloza
.
#covÄ±d19 #quarantine #vpuanecdotes", [('spa', 1.0)])

text:
('3 WAKTU TIDAK DIGALAKKAN MANDI :

1. 30 minit selepas solat Asar.

2. Selepas Maghrib.

3. Selepas Isyak sehingga 12 malam.

Penjelasan :

1. 30 minit selepas solat asar.

Adalah waktu dimana darah dalam badan panas, jika kita mandi ketika itu, akan menyebabkan badan menjadi letih dan penat untuk bekerja.

2. Lepas Maghrib

Jantung kita sudah mulai lemah untuk bekerja. 
Kajian menunjukkan bahawa ketika ini jika kita mandi akan menyebabkan paru-paru boleh dimasuki air dan boleh menyebabkan penyakit paru-paru berair.

3. Selepas solat Isyak

Ini masanya jantung berehat, jika mandi ketika ini akan mengakibatkan lemah jantung.
Sebaiknya mandi selepas jam 1 pagi.

Antara pukul 2~3 pagi, itu akan lebih memberikan tenaga kepada badan seperti bateri yang telah lemah dicas semula.

Kata Alim Ulamak :-*

Û Surah Al-Fatihah dapat memadam kemurkaan Allah swt.

Û Surah Yasin dapat menghilangkan dahaga dan haus di Padang Masyar.

Û Surah Dukhan dapat membantu kita ketika menghadapi ujian Allah swt pada hari kiamat.

Û Surah Al-Waqiâ€™ah dapat melindungi kita daripada ditimpa kesusahan atau kemiskinan semasa hidup di dunia.

Û Surah Al-Mulk dapat meringankan azab kubur.

Û Surah Al-Kautsar dapat mendamaikan segala perbalahan dan merapatkan silaturahim.

Û Surah Al-Kafirun dapat menghalang kita daripada menjadi kafir ketika menghadapi kematian. (Husnul Khatimah)

Û Surah Al-Ikhlas dapat melindungi kita daripada jadi golongan munafik.

Û Surah Al-Falak dapat menghapuskan perasaan hasad dengki dan irihati.

Û Surah An-Nas dapat melindungi kita daripada ditimpa penyakit nyanyok dan was-was.

Seterusnya, bagi melawan syaitan durjana.

Dikatakan juga:-

Û Ketika anda membawa Al-Qur'an, syaitan hanya tengok saja.

Û Ketika anda duduk dan membukanya, syaitan mula curiga.

Û Ketika anda membacanya, syaitan mula gelisah.

Û Ketika anda mengalun ayat2 suci dgn merdu, betul tajwid, menghayati dan memahaminya, iblis & syaitan mula kejang.

Û Bila kita mengamalkan Al-Qur'an dalam kehidupan seharian, dia kena stroke.

Teruskan membaca Al-Qur'an dan mengamalkannya agar iblis, syaitan dan anak beranak suku sakatnya terus stroke.

Tahukah anda, dimanakah hospital yg menyembuhkan anak beranak suku sakat kaum iblis syaitan yg kena stroke dan luka2 terkena kerikil panas semasa azan.

Jawapannya ialah di dalam *jamban & tandas* menunggu & menanti orang Islam yg kencing berdiri. Bila mereka melihat org Islam kencing berdiri, tambah pula tidak baca doa masuk tandas, maka mereka berebut-rebut, tolak menolak, tendang menendang untuk kena air kencing. Jadi, jika anda kencing berdiri, anda menjadi doktor yg menyembuh dan memelihara syaitan.

Û Ketika anda ingin menyebarkan pesanan ini, syaitan pun mencegahnya.

Û Syaitan kata;
_"Jangan sebar kerana ianya tiada kepentingan langsung."_

Pilihan dihujung jari anda, samada hendak disebarkan atau hanya alongside dalam gadget anda, kemudian delete, terpulanglah.', '3 BATH TIMES NOT ENCOURAGED:

1. 30 minutes after Asr prayer.

2. After Maghrib.

3. After Isyak until 12 pm.

Explanation:

1. 30 minutes after Asr prayer.

It is a time when the blood in the body is hot, if we take a shower at that time, it will cause the body to become tired and tired to work.

2. After Maghrib

Our hearts are beginning to weaken to work.
Studies show that at this point if we take a shower will cause the lungs to enter the water and can cause watery lung disease.

3. After Isyak prayer

This is the time for the heart to rest, if taking a bath at this time will result in heart failure.
It is best to take a shower after 1 am.

Between 2 ~ 3 in the morning, it will give more energy to the body like a battery that has been weakly recharged.

Says Alim Ulamak:-*

Û Surah Al-Fatihah can erase the wrath of Allah swt.

Û Surah Yasin can quench thirst and thirst in Padang Masyar.

Û Surah Dukhan can help us when facing the test of Allah swt on the Day of Judgment.

Û Surah Al-Waqiâ€™ah can protect us from hardship or poverty while living in the world.

Û Surah Al-Mulk can alleviate the torment of the grave.

Û Surah Al-Kautsar can reconcile all disputes and strengthen friendship.

Û Surah Al-Kafirun can prevent us from becoming disbelievers in the face of death. (Husnul Khatimah)

Û Surah Al-Ikhlas can protect us from being hypocrites.

Û Surah Al-Falak can eliminate feelings of envy and jealousy.

Û Surah An-Nas can protect us from the disease of senility and anxiety.

Next, to fight the evil devil.

It is also said:-

Û When you bring the Qur'an, the devil just looks.

Û As you sit down and open it, the devil starts to get suspicious.

Û As you read it, the devil starts to get restless.

Û When you recite the holy verses with melody, correct tajwid, appreciate and understand it, iblis & satan start to convulse.

Û When we practice the Qur'an in daily life, he has a stroke.

Continue to read the Qur'an and practice it so that the devil, satan and the children of the sakat tribe continue to stroke.

Do you know, where is the hospital that heals the children of the sakat tribe of the devils who had strokes and wounds hit by hot pebbles during the call to prayer.

The answer is in the * toilet & toilet * waiting & waiting for Muslims who urinate standing up. When they see Muslims urinating standing up, in addition to not reciting the prayer to go to the toilet, then they scramble, push push, kick kick to get urine. So, if you urinate standing up, you become a doctor who heals and keeps the devil alive.

Û When you want to spread this message, the devil also prevents it.

Û Satan says;
_ "Don't spread it because it has no direct interest." _

The choice is at your fingertips, whether to spread or just alongside in your gadget, then delete, is up to you.', [('msa', 1.0)])
